public class VirtualDatacenter
extends DomainWithLimitsWrapper<com.abiquo.server.core.cloud.VirtualDatacenterDto>

Represents a virtual datacenter.

Virtual datacenters expose a set of compute, storage and networking resources that can be consumed by the tenants.

Author:
Ignasi Barrera, Francesc Montserrat
See Also:
http://community.abiquo.com/display/ABI20/Virtual+Datacenter+Resource
